'''比佛利山酒店'''（The Beverly Hills Hotel）是位于美国加利福尼亚州[[比弗利山_(加利福尼亚州)|比佛利山]]的一个酒店，由美籍建築師{{link-en|埃爾默·格雷|Elmer Grey}}（{{lang|en|Elmer Grey}}）設計，于1912年5月12日开张。<ref name="gebhard">David Gebhard, ''An Architectural Guidebook to Los Ángeles'', Layton, Utah: Gibbs Smith, 2003, p. 152 [http://books.google.fr/books?id=WWl29hn0C9gC&pg=PA152&dq=%22burton+E.+Green%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=oqJqUePXMcS5hAfD4YDICw&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22burton%20E.%20Green%22&f=false] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.fr/books?id=WWl29hn0C9gC&pg=PA152&dq=%22burton+E.+Green%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=oqJqUePXMcS5hAfD4YDICw&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22burton%20E.%20Green%22&f=false |date=20190613001400 }}</ref><ref name="maureencallahan">{{cite news |first=Maureen |last=Callahan |url=http://nypost.com/2014/05/17/a-night-at-the-deserted-blacklisted-beverly-hills-hotel/ |title=A night at the vacant Beverly Hills Hotel |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Post|The New York Post]] |date=2014-05-17 |accessdate=2014-05-17 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211015424/https://nypost.com/2014/05/17/a-night-at-the-deserted-blacklisted-beverly-hills-hotel/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

